if-starc-can-sunil-gavaskar-on-how-aussie-pacer-can-justify-his-hefty-ipl-price-tag%2Farticleshow%2F107603723.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders'%20whopping%20IPL%20bid%20of%20Rs%2024.75%20crore%20for%20Australian%20pacer%20Mitchell%20Starc%20surprised%20the%20cricketing%20community.%20Even%20the%20legendary%20Indian%20cricketer%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20expressed%20his%20opinion%2C%20stating%20that%20no%20player%20is%20deserving%20of%20such%20a%20substantial%20amount.%20Gavaskar%20added%20that%20Starc%20will%20need%20to%20deliver%20an%20exceptional%20performance%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20to%20justify%20the%20hefty%20paycheque.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20anybody%20is%20worth%20that%20kind%20of%20money.%20If%20Starc%20can%20make%20an%20impact%20and%20win%20maybe%20four%20out%20of%20the%2014%20matches%20that%20he%20plays%2C%20then%20you%20can%20say%20money's%20worth.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Pak%20Armed%2C%20Trained%20Assam%20Insurgents%20And%20Sent%20Them%20Back%20To%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan%20armed%20and%20trained%20the%20first%20batch%20of%20insurgents%20of%20the%20United%20Liberation%20Front%20of%20Asom%20(ULFA)%20in%201991-92%2C%20and%20sent%20them%20back%20to%20India%20to%20stir%20trouble%20in%20the%20northeast%20region%2C%20according%20to%20writer%20and%20researcher%20Rajeev%20Bhattacharyya%2C%20whose%20latest%20work%20details%20the%20untold%20story%20of%20the%20outlawed%20separatist%20outfit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%201996%20and%202004%2C%20insurgents%20from%20outfits%20in%20the%20northeast%20such%20as%20the%20NDFB%2C%20PLA%2C%20and%20ATTF%20were%20trained%20at%20different%20locations%20in%20Pakistan%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20assembling%20bombs%20through%20sophisticated%20technology%2C%20Mr%20Bhattacharyya%20says%20in%20'ULFA%3A%20The%20Mirage%20of%20Dawn'%2C%20based%20on%20interviews%20with%20ULFA%20members%20in%20the%20northeast%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20former%20officers%20engaged%20in%20counter-insurgency%20operations%2C%20as%20well%20as%20papers%20of%20ULFA%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20estimated%20that%20around%20a%20hundred%20rebel%20functionaries%20had%20received%20the%20training%20during%20this%20period.%20One%20ULFA%20batch%20was%20also%20taken%20to%20Tora%20Bora%20in%20Afghanistan%20for%20training.%20The%20modules%20offered%20to%20the%20rebel%20groups%20were%20of%20different%20durations%2C%20ranging%20from%2017%20days%20to%20three%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhattacharyya%20says%20in%20the%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20batch%20of%20ULFA%20militants%20was%20trained%20in%20Pakistan%20in%201991-92%20in%20three%20groups%20comprising%20a%20total%20of%20about%2040%20functionaries.%20One%20group%20was%20trained%20near%20Peshawar%20and%20other%20functionaries%20were%20taken%20for%20short%20visits%20to%20Kandahar%20in%20Afghanistan%20and%20the%20arms%20bazaar%20at%20Darra%20Adam%20Khel%20near%20the%20Safed%20Koh%20mountains%20in%20Pakistan%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%20in%20the%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20Lieutenant%20General%20Asfaq%20Pervez%20Kayani%2C%20who%20was%20later%20appointed%20chief%20of%20the%20espionage%20agency%20Inter-Services%20Intelligence%20(ISI)%2C%20interacted%20and%20shook%20hands%20with%20a%20batch%20of%20ULFA%20functionaries%20when%20they%20were%20undergoing%20training%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Mr%20Bhattacharyya%20says.%20Lt%20General%20Kayani%20succeeded%20General%20Pervez%20Musharraf%20as%20Pakistan's%20army%20chief%20in%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhattacharyya's%20account%20delves%20into%20all%20major%20episodes%2C%20delineates%20their%20causes%20and%20effects%2C%20and%20debunks%20interpretations%20about%20the%20ULFA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20part%20about%20ULFA%20(Independent)%20chief%20Paresh%20Baruah%20surviving%20four%20assassination%20attempts%20in%20Bangladesh%20would%20be%20of%20great%20interest%20to%20researchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20attempt%20was%20made%20at%20ULFA's%20camp%20in%20Bangladesh's%20Satcherri%20when%20an%20assassin%20was%20sent%20by%20Special%20Branch%20of%20Assam%20police%20to%20kill%20Baruah.%20However%2C%20he%20escaped%20from%20the%20camp%20before%20he%20could%20pull%20the%20trigger%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhattacharyya%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20second%20attempt%20was%20made%20by%20a%20senior%20officer%20of%20the%20Assam%20Police%2C%20who%20got%20in%20touch%20with%20a%20criminal%20syndicate%20in%20Bangladesh%20to%20gun%20down%20Baruah%2C%20which%20failed.%20The%20same%20officer%20had%20also%20convinced%20an%20ULFA%20functionary%20turned%20mole%20named%20Munna%20Mishra%20to%20cross%20the%20border%20into%20Bangladesh%20and%20target%20Baruah.%20This%20attempt%20proved%20futile%20as%20well...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhattacharyya%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fourth%20attempt%20was%20in%20Dhaka%20when%20a%20boulder%20was%20hurled%20by%20an%20unknown%20person%20at%20Baruah%20at%20a%20crowded%20place%20in%20the%20car%20he%20was%20travelling.%20Baruah%20escaped%20unhurt%2C%20although%20the%20windscreen%20of%20the%20vehicle%20was%20damaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707658140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fodvq6f3g_ulfa_625x300_11_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fulfa-mirage-of-dawn-when-pakistan-armed-trained-assam-insurgents-ulfa-and-sent-them-back-to-india-5037838%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20armed%20and%20trained%20the%20first%20batch%20of%20insurgents%20of%20the%20United%20Liberation%20Front%20of%20Asom%20(ULFA)%20in%201991-92%2C%20and%20sent%20them%20back%20to%20India%20to%20stir%20trouble%20in%20the%20northeast%20region%2C%20according%20to%20writer%20and%20researcher%20Rajeev%20Bhattacharyya.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22