%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F60643-kona-srikar-bharat-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKS%20Bharat%3C%2Fa%3E's%20role%20in%20the%20Test%20team.%20Since%20making%20his%20Test%20debut%20last%20year%20against%20Australia%20in%20Nagpur%2C%20Bharat%20has%20scored%20just%20221%20runs%20in%20seven%20matches%2C%20averaging%20a%20meagre%2020.09.%20He%20is%20yet%20to%20score%20a%20half-century%20in%20the%20longest%20format%20of%20the%20game.%20Manjrekar%20feels%20since%20Bharat%20is%20not%20contributing%20much%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20the%20management%20should%20look%20at%20other%20alternatives.%20Manjrekar%20doesn't%20feel%20the%20management%20should%20invest%20more%20time%20in%20Bharat%2C%20especially%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rishabh%20Pant%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107048-rishabh-pant-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERishabh%20Pant%3C%2Fa%3E%20waiting%20in%20the%20wings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20lot%20like%20he's%20playing%20his%20first%20series.%20He's%20played%20before%3B%20he%20played%20all%20four%20Test%20matches%20against%20Australia%2C%20and%20Rishabh%20Pant%20is%20due%20to%20come%20any%20time%20soon.%20So%2C%20I%20am%20not%20sure%20whether%20it%20is%20worthwhile%20and%20makes%20sense%20to%20keep%20investing%20in%20KS%20Bharat.%20He's%20also%20not%2020%20years%20old%2C%20and%20India%20had%20moved%20on%20from%20KS%20Bharat%20and%20gone%20to%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishan%20Kishan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107047-ishan-kishan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIshan%20Kishan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%20he's%20done%20just%20enough%20to%20maybe%20just%20keep%20his%20place%20in%20the%20side.%20This%20team%20management%20believes%20in%20being%20fair%20to%20every%20individual%2C%20but%20I%20would%20personally%20look%20at%20another%20option%20before%20Rishabh%20Pant%20comes%20in%20and%20takes%20his%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Manjrekar%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DX7npvCpRKbE%5C%22%3EESPNcricinfo%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManjrekar%20urged%20the%20management%20to%20focus%20on%20keepers%20who%20can%20contribute%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20rather%20than%20his%20glovework.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20will%20start%20looking%20at%20KS%20Bharat%20whether%20his%20keeping%20is%20that%20good%20we%20can%20afford%20to%20have%20somebody%20who%20is%20not%20contributing%20as%20much%20with%20the%20bat...%20India%20of%20late%20and%20the%20world%20over%2C%20if%20you%20see%20is%20going%20for%20keepers%20who%20are%20decent%20keepers%20but%20contribute%20with%20the%20bat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20finalise%20a%20wicketkeeper%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20Pant%2C%20who%20continues%20his%20recovery%20after%20suffering%20a%20life-threatening%20car%20crash%20in%20December%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPant%20has%20began%20light%20training%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20play%20some%20part%20in%20the%20upcoming%20season%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL).%20He%20was%20retained%20by%20Delhi%20Capitals%20during%20the%20mini%20auction%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Capitals%20(DC)%20IPL%202024%20squad%3A%20Abhishek%20Porel%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Anrich%20Nortje%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64072-anrich-nortje-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAnrich%20Nortje%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Axar%20Patel%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63024-akshar-rajeshbhai-patel-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAxar%20Patel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22David%20Warner%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1285-david-warner-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDavid%20Warner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishant%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F900-ishant-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIshant%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3