66%2Fmissouri-mom-bakes-baby-death-oven-crime%5C%22%3EDaily%20Express%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3EA%20burnt%20baby%20blanket%20was%20also%20found%20at%20the%20scene.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20did%20not%20provide%20further%20clarification%20on%20how%20such%20an%20error%20occurred.%20Other%20circumstances%20around%20the%20incident%20have%20also%20not%20been%20revealed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20baby's%20mother%20identified%20as%2026-year-old%20Mariah%20Thomas%2C%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20endangering%20the%20welfare%20of%20a%20child.%C2%A0According%20to%20the%20Jackson%20County%20Prosecutor's%20Office%2C%20Thomas%20''faces%20the%20Class%20A%20felony%20of%20Endangering%20the%20Welfare%20of%20a%20Child%20in%20the%201st%20Degree%2C%20Death%20of%20a%20Child.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20appreciate%20all%20first%20responders%20who%20worked%20this%20scene%20and%20the%20prosecutors%20who%20went%20to%20the%20scene%20to%20issue%20these%20charges.%20We%20acknowledge%20the%20gruesome%20nature%20of%20this%20tragedy%20and%20our%20hearts%20are%20weighted%20by%20the%20loss%20of%20this%20precious%20life.%20We%20trust%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%20to%20respond%20appropriately%20to%20these%20awful%20circumstances%2C''%20Jackson%20County%20prosecuting%20attorney%20Jean%20Peters%20Baker%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20friend%20of%20the%20mother%20suggested%20Ms%20Thomas'%20mental%20health%20may%20have%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20tragedy.%20They%20described%20the%20baby%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20bubbly%26quot%3B%20child%20who%20was%20%26quot%3Bsmiling%20all%20the%20time%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Thomas%20is%20currently%20being%20held%20at%20the%C2%A0Jackson%20County%20Detention%20Center.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707656580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Ff9g3bq1o_mariah-thomas_625x300_11_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22origi