ve%20with%20severe%20trauma%20to%20her%20body.%20She%20was%20rushed%20to%C2%A0Bellevue%20Hospital%20where%20she%20was%20pronounced%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20it's%20not%20clear%C2%A0whether%20she%20was%20an%20NYU%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustina%20Sung%2C%2030%2C%20who%20was%20in%20her%20nearby%20apartment%20at%20the%20time%20said%20that%20she%20heard%20''a%C2%A0thump%20and%20girl%20scream.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20roommate%20asked%20someone%20and%20someone%20said%20%5Bthey%5D%20jumped%20off%20and%20landed%20in%20that%20triangle%20area%2C''%20Ms%20Sung%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20small%2C%20fenced-in%20green%20space%20outside%20of%20the%20building%20at%20the%20confluence%20of%209th%20and%20Stuyvesant%20Streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20police%C2%A0at%20the%20scene%20are%20investigating%20the%20blood-splattered%20area%20just%20outside%20of%20the%20fencing.%20Circumstances%20surrounding%20her%20death%20remain%20shrouded%20in%20mystery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20alarming%20trend%2C%C2%A0US%20suicide%20rates%20have%20ticked%20up%20almost%20every%20year.%20More%20than%2050%2C000%20Americans%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%202023%2C%20more%20than%20any%20year%20on%20record%2C%20as%20per%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fmeet-the-press%2Fvideo%2Fmore-than-50-000-americans-died-by-suicide-in-2023-more-than-any-year-on-record-201161285832%5C%22%3E%20%3Ci%3ENBC%20News.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Mental%20health%20officials%20said%20it%20is%20the%20highest%20rate%20of%20suicide%20that%20the%20nation%20has%20ever%20seen%2C%20and%20attributed%20the%20role%20of%20post-pandemic%20effects%20as%20the%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20tragic%2C%20we%20started%20to%20see%20a%20big%20increase%20in%20suicide%20deaths%20during%20the%20opioid%20epidemic.%20That%20was%20worsened%20by%20Covid%20and%20unfortunately%2C%20those%20rates%20have%20continued%20to%20increase%2C''%20Luke%20Engeriser%2C%20Deputy%20Chief%20