0by%20Khan's%20Pakistan%20Tahreek-e-Insaaf%20(PTI)%2C%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjailed-ex-pak-pm-imran-khan-gets-bail-in-12-cases-linked-to-may-9-violence-case-5031350%5C%22%3Eas%20he%20serves%20time%20in%20jai%3C%2Fa%3El.%20Though%20Khan%20himself%20was%20barred%20from%20contesting%20due%20to%20a%20conviction%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%2C%20PTI%20candidates%2C%20who%20had%20to%20contest%20as%20independents%2C%20won%2091%20seats%20in%20the%20National%20Assembly.%20Though%20they%20are%20far%20from%20wresting%20power%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-election-results-2024-imran-khan-backed-independents-go-to-court-challenge-pakistan-poll-results-report-5034832%5C%22%3Ethe%20result%20%3C%2Fa%3Eindicates%20the%20success%20of%20a%20risky%20political%20strategy%20deployed%20by%20Khan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fpeople%2Fimran-khan-from-cricket-to-jail-with-layover-at-prime-ministers-office-5010784%5C%22%3Esince%20his%20ouster%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20in%20April%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnTaking%20On%20The%20Military%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20played%20out%20in%20this%20election%20was%20eerily%20similar%20to%20what%20transpired%20in%202018.%20Only%2C%20the%20protagonists%20were%20differently%20placed.%20It%20was%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20who%20was%20sentenced%20to%20prison%20less%20than%20three%20weeks%20before%20the%20polls%20and%20Khan%20enjoyed%20the%20backing%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-election-results-imran-khan-bilwal-bhutto-nawaz-sharif-no-clear-winner-in-pakistan-yet-imran-khan-party-protests-delay-in-results-5035050%5C%22%3Emilitary%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20allegations%20of%20the%20election%20not%20being%20free%20and%20fair%20were%20also%20similar%2C%20and%20the%20military%20was%20explicitly%20accused%20of%20interfering%20in%20the%20process%20to%20prop%20its%20blue-eyed%20boy%2C%20Khan%2C%20to%20the%20premiership.%20Khan%20ultimately%20became%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20but%20his%20relationship%20with%20the%20all-powerful%20military%20soured%20within%20four%20years%20as%20he%20was%20seen%20to%20be%20meddling%20in%20the%20supposed%20civilian%20no-go%20zone%20of%20military%20and%20ISI%20(Inter-Services%20Intelligence)%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20out%20of%20power%2C%20Khan%20took%20on%20the%20military%20in%20an%20unprecedented%20manner.%20Within%20a%20month%20of%20being%20ousted%2C%20he%20led%20a%20%26quot%3Blong%20march%26quot%3B%20into%20Islamabad%20that%20turned%20violent.%20Another%20one%20in%20November%202022%20saw%20him%20being%20shot%20in%20the%20leg%20by%20a%20gunman%20who%20opened%20fire%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Wazirabad.%20Khan%20accused%20a%20senior%20army%20official%2C%20Major%20General%20Faisal%20Naseer%2C%20of%20the%20attempted%20assassination%20bid.%20In%20a%20rare%20statement%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20military%20rebutted%20the%20allegation%20by%20Khan.%20It%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20has%20been%20a%20consistent%20pattern%20for%20the%20last%20one%20year%20where%20military%20and%20intelligence%20agencies%20officials%20are%20targeted%20with%20insinuations%20and%20sensational%20propaganda%20for%20the%20furtherance%20of%20political%20objectives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan's%20constant%20tirades%20against%20the%20military%20saw%20an%20unusual%20and%20perhaps%20unimaginable%20outcome.%20The%20military%2C%20a%20formidable%20and%20unopposed%20power%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20saw%20violent%20attacks%20against%20itself%20in%20May%202023.%20Protesters%20took%20to%20the%20streets%20after%20Khan's%20arrest%20and%20were%20seen%20not%20just%20attacking%20the%20police%20and%20government%20buildings%20but%20also%20military%20installations.%20Shockingly%2C%20the%20army%20headquarters%20and%20an%20air%20force%20base%20were%20targeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20one%20of%20the%20few%20early%20indications%20that%20Khan's%20political%20gamble%20of%20taking%20on%20the%20military%20had%20paid%20off.%20It%20was%20yielding%20dividends%2C%20and%20Khan's%20PTI%20was%20hopeful%20that%20it%20would%20bear%20even%20electoral%20dividends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhipping%20up%20anti-US%20sentiment%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Pakistan%20economy%20tanked%20and%20Khan%20made%20an%20unceremonious%20exit%20from%20power%2C%20he%20trained%20his%20guns%20at%20the%20United%20States.%20Khan%20not%20only%20accused%20the%20US%20of%20being%20behind%20his%20ouster%20but%20also%20singled%20out%20US%20Assistant%20Secretary%20of%20State%20for%20South%20and%20Central%20Asian%20Affairs%2C%20Donald%20Lu%2C%20for%20conveying%20the%20same%20to%20the%20then-Pakistan%20ambassador%20to%20the%20US%2C%20Asad%20Majeed%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20Khan%20himself%20said%20that%20Lu%20told%20Majeed%20Khan%20there%20would%20be%20implications%20if%20Khan%20was%20not%20removed.%20The%20meeting%2C%20as%20revealed%20later%2C%20had%20taken%20place%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20Khan's%20visit%20to%20Moscow%20just%20as%20Russia%20attacked%20Ukraine%2C%20gravely%20upsetting%20Washington%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Khan%20continued%20to%20use%20the%20argument%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bforeign%20conspiracy%26quot%3B%20behind%20his%20defeat%20in%20the%20no-confidence%20motion.%20The%20US%20denied%20the%20allegation%20of%20interference%20in%20Pakistani%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20victory%20of%20Khan's%20candidates%2C%20the%20US%20State%20Department%20released%20a%20statement%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20is%20prepared%20to%20work%20with%20the%20next%20Pakistani%20government%2C%20regardless%20of%20political%20party%2C%20to%20advance%20our%20shared%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20expressing%20concern%20over%20the%20allegations%20of%20election%20fraud%20-%20%26quot%3Bclaims%20of%20interference%20or%20fraud%20should%20be%20fully%20investigated%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EPlaying%20Up%20The%20'Outsider'%20Threat%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20Khan%20successfully%20played%20on%20anti-US%20sentiment%20in%20some%20segments%20of%20Pakistani%20society.%20Even%20though%20at%20one%20point%20he%20seemed%20to%20have%20taken%20a%20U-turn%20when%20he%20told%20the%20Financial%20Times%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20I'm%20concerned%2C%20it's%20over%2C%20it's%20behind%20me.%20The%20Pakistan%20I%20want%20to%20lead%20must%20have%20good%20relationships%20with%20everyone%2C%20especially%20the%20United%20States%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20had%20already%20fanned%20the%20embers%20of%20discontent%20and%20anger%20that%20had%20taken%20root%20in%20some%20places%20since%20the%20'war%20on%20terror'%20days.%20Khan%20used%20it%20as%20a%20political%20tool%20to%20fuel%20suspicion%20against%20an%20outsider%20meddling%20in%20Pakistan's%20internal%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%2C%20therefore%2C%20seems%20to%20have%20put%20to%20use%20a%20political%20strategy%20that's%20fraught%20with%20the%20danger%20of%20backfiring%20in%20order%20to%20make%20a%20political%20mark%20in%20dire%20circumstances.%20It%20may%20not%20lead%20to%20any%20immediate%2C%20direct%20benefits%20in%20terms%20of%20political%20power%2C%20but%20it%20perhaps%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20keep%20his%20support%20base%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3E(Maha%20Siddiqui%20is%20a%20journalist%20who%20has%20extensively%20reported%20on%20public%20policy%20and%20global%20affairs.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707639960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F1tp9bpt8_pakistan-elections-generic-imran-khan-afp_625x300_10_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-imran-khans-twin-strike-on-us-and-pak-army-helped-him-5036430%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20result%20of%20the%20elections%20indicates%20the%20success%20of%20a%20risky%20political%20strategy%20deployed%20by%20Khan%20since%20his%20ouster%20in%20April%202022.%20It%20may%20not%20win%20him%20political%20power%2C%20but%20it%20may%20just%20be%20enough%20to%20keep%20his%20support%20base%20intact.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-imran-khans-twin-strike-on-us-and-pak-army-helped-him-5036430%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-imran-khans-twin-strike-on-us-and-pak-army-helped-him-5036430%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-imran-khans-twin-strike-on-us-and-pak-army-helped-him-5036430%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Yatra%20Delaying%20INDIA%20Seats%20Decisions%3F%20Sachin%20Pilot's%20Reply%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20some%20INDIA%20bloc%20constituents%20switching%20sides%20to%20the%20NDA%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Sachin%20Pilot%20today%20said%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20is%20%26quot%3Bstrong%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20BJP%20is%20attempting%20a%20%26quot%3Bfrantic%20rejig%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20political%20landscape%20as%20it%20is%20worried%20over%20the%20collective%20strength%20of%20the%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20PTI%2C%20Mr%20Pilot%20also%20said%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Trinamool%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20very%20much%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%2C%20and%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20a%20way%20forward%20will%20be%20found%20in%20seat-sharing%20talks%20with%20her%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20BJP%20talking%20about%20370%20seats%20for%20itself%20and%20400-plus%20for%20the%20NDA%20was%20more%20of%20%26quot%3Bbravado%20and%20rhetoric%26quot%3B%20than%20a%20practical%20assessment%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Rahul%20Gandhi-led%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20travels%20through%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20the%20AICC%20general%20secretary%20in-charge%20of%20the%20state%20dismissed%20suggestions%20that%20the%20yatra%20was%20adversely%20affecting%20the%20poll%20preparations%20of%20the%20party%20and%20asserted%20that%20talks%20for%20seat-sharing%20with%20allies%20were%20going%20on%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20speak%2C%20we%20are%20finalising%20seat-sharing%20agreements%20with%20most%20of%20our%20allies%20in%20different%20states.%20So%20it%20is%20not%20a%20question%20of%20either%2For.%20The%20yatra%20is%20going%20on%20but%20other%20things%20are%20being%20handled%20by%20the%20AICC%20leadership%20and%20the%20state%20in-charges.%20The%20Congress%20president%20(Mallikarjun%20Kharge)%20is%20himself%20overseeing%20all%20these%20meetings%20and%20negotiations%20that%20are%20being%20held%2C%26quot%3B%20Pilot%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20attempt%20is%20to%20make%20sure%20we%20fight%20unitedly.%20Yes%20we%20have%20had%20some%20that%20have%20left%20our%20alliance%20but%20largely%20the%20alliance%20is%20intact%20and%20very%20soon%20we%20will%20be%20announcing%20the%20seat%20sharing%20and%20a%20future%20roadmap%20that%20the%20alliance%20will%20come%20up%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20suggestions%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20unravelling%20with%20JD(U)%20chief%20Nitish%20Kumar%20crossing%20over%20to%20the%20NDA%2C%20RLD's%20Jayant%20Chaudhary's%20imminent%20switch-over%20and%20Ms%20Banerjee%20attacking%20the%20Congress%2C%20Mr%20Pilot%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLook%20at%20the%20amount%20of%20partners%20that%20left%20the%20NDA%20'%26quot%3B%20Akali%20Dal%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20PDP%2C%20AIADMK.%20So%20the%20number%20of%20those%20leaving%20the%20NDA%20is%20far%20larger%20than%20some%20of%20those%20people%20who%20may%20not%20be%20with%20us%20today.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20strong%20and%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20we%20are%20having%20discussions%20with%20the%20TMC%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2046-year-old%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20switchover%20to%20the%20NDA%20raises%20the%20question%20of%20credibility%20also%20and%20he%20would%20have%20to%20answer%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Bihar%20when%20he%20goes%20to%20polls.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20may%20come%20and%20go%2C%20one%20or%20two%20moving%20sides%20will%20not%20make%20an%20impact%20on%20the%20effort%20we%20are%20putting%20in%20as%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%26quot%3B%20A%20one-on-one%20contest%20between%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20and%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20is%20tilted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20opposition%20coalition%2C%20Mr%20Pilot%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20assure%20you%20that%20with%20regards%20to%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20the%20final%20outcome%20will%20be%20a%20positive%20one.%20Every%20political%20party%20has%20its%20own%20turf%20to%20protect.%20A%20regional%20party%20will%20not%20want%20to%20cede%20too%20much%20space%2C%20as%20a%20national%20party%2C%20we%20also%20have%20an%20obligation%20to%20our%20state%20units.%20So%20there%20is%20always%20going%20to%20be%20some%20give%20and%20take.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20the%20sensitivities%20of%20each%20of%20our%20partners%20but%20the%20final%20objective%20of%20the%20alliance%20is%20to%20come%20together%20and%20present%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20country%2C%20and%20we%20will%20achieve%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20%26quot%3Bstrong%26quot%3B%20and%20very%20soon%20it%20will%20announce%20the%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20in%20different%20states%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20alliance%20will%20pose%20a%20%26quot%3Bformidable%20challenge%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20arithmetic%20calculation%20will%20show%20that%20the%20vote%20share%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20was%20over%2060%20per%20cent%20in%20the%202019%20elections%20and%20that%20of%20the%20NDA%20was%20around%2035%20per%20cent%2C%20therefore%2C%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20does%20not%20come%20together%20whether%20it%20is%20by%20using%20central%20agencies%2C%20misinformation%2C%20propaganda%20or%20pressure%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLargely%20all%20this%20is%20futile%20because%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20strong.%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20part%20of%20the%20alliance%20and%20her%20primary%20objective%20is%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20will%20work%20together%20and%20find%20a%20way%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20Pilot%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20there%20is%20a%20cause%20for%20worry%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20therefore%20%26quot%3Bthis%20frantic%20rejigging%20of%20the%20political%20landscape%20is%20happening%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20recent%20statement%20in%20Parliament%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20get%20370%20seats%20and%20the%20NDA%20over%20400%2C%20Mr%20Pilot%20said%20Parliament%20is%20for%20discussing%20policy%20and%20legislation%20but%20that%20platform%20was%20used%20to%20make%20a%20purely%20political%20speech%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20sort%20of%20bravado%20and%20chest-thumping.%20I%20think%20the%20people%20of%20India%20will%20decide%20and%20no%20election%20is%20won%20or%20lost%20till%20the%20last%20vote%20is%20counted.%20I%20have%20great%20faith%20in%20the%20wisdom%20and%20objectivity%20of%20our%20voters%2C%20they%20know%20the%20difference%20between%20truth%20and%20propaganda%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%20coming%20together%20is%20certainly%20a%20worry%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20this%20thing%20about%20%26quot%3B300%20paar%2C%20400%20paar%26quot%3B%20is%20more%20rhetoric%20than%20a%20true%20reflection%20of%20reality%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pilot%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP's%20poll%20plank%20is%20very%20unclear%20as%20it%20is%20not%20going%20to%20the%20people%20with%20its%2010-year%20report%20card%20or%20with%20a%20blueprint%20on%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20%26quot%3Brecord%20unemployment%2C%20skyrocketing%20inflation%2C%20agrarian%20distress%20and%20ever-increasing%20gap%20between%20the%20rich%20and%20poor%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20not%20come%20through%20on%20their%20commitments%20for%20doubling%20farmers'%20income%2C%20providing%20jobs%2C%20legal%20framework%20for%20MSP%2C%20or%20on%20eradicating%20black%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707639960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F4vid6gvo_sachin-pilot_625x300_11_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-sachin-pilot-india-rahul-gandhis-yatra-delaying-india-seats-decisions-sachin-pilots-reply-5036392%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20some%20INDIA%20bloc%20constituents%20switching%20sides%20to%20the%20NDA%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Sachin%20Pilot%20today%20said%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20is%20%26quot%3Bstrong%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20BJP%20is%20attempting%20a%20%26quot%3Bfrantic%20rejig%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20political%20landscape%20as%20it%20is%20worried%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-sachin-pilot-india-rahul-gandhis-yatra-delaying-india-seats-decisions-sachin-pilots-reply-5036392%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-c