%20can%20endure%20150%20kgs%20of%20weight%20and%20can%20last%20more%20than%2020%20years.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341211%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20chair%20can%20endure%20150%20kg%20of%20weight%20and%20can%20last%20more%20than%2020%20years.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20chair%2C%20Ankit%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20polish%20on%20the%20chair%20is%20done%20using%20natural%20oils.%20It%20can%20endure%20weights%20of%20more%20than%20150%20kg%2C%20and%20the%20furniture%20has%20also%20been%20treated%20to%20protect%20against%20any%20kind%20of%20insects.%20The%20life%20of%20the%20chair%20is%20up%20to%2020%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnkit%20does%20not%20want%20to%20commercialise%20the%20chair.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20received%20numerous%20inquiries%20about%20whether%20I%20am%20selling%20these%20chairs.%20However%2C%20my%20goal%20is%20not%20profit%20or%20loss.%20My%20aim%20is%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20provide%20training%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20working%20on%20a%20proposal%20to%20present%20to%20my%20university%20to%20initiate%20a%20program%20where%20individuals%20can%20come%20and%20learn%20how%20to%20make%20chairs%20and%20collaborate%20with%20me%20to%20create%20more%20furniture.%20This%20approach%20will%20al