ommunities%20and%20authorities%20with%20the%20tools%20needed%20for%20effective%20water%20resource%20management%20and%20remediation.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20found%20that%20while%20working%20with%20one%20of%20his%20PhD%20objectives%20%E2%80%94%20where%20he%20was%20focusing%20on%20the%20development%20of%20an%20advanced%20bio-oxidation%20system%20for%20water%20remediation%20%E2%80%94%20he%20realised%20that%20there%20were%20very%20limited%20multiparametric%20devices%20available%20to%20promptly%20check%20the%20quality%20of%20water%20in%20real-time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20motivated%20me%20to%20channel%20my%20efforts%20into%20creating%20a%20solution%20that%20would%20not%20only%20aid%20in%20my%20research%20but%20also%20serve%20the%20broader%20community%20by%20providing%20an%20affordable%2C%20real-time%2C%20and%20multi-parametric%20water%20quality%20monitoring%20tool%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20it%20work%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20features%20of%20this%20IoT-enabled%20real-time%20water%20monitoring%20system%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%97%8F%20Integrated%20GPS%3A%20Enables%20precise%20location%20tracking%20of%20water%20quality%20metrics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%97%8F%20Diverse%20Sensors%3A%20Measures%20turbidity%2C%20Total%20Dissolved%20Solids%20(TDS)%2C%20oxygen%20levels%2C%20temperature%2C%20and%20pressure%20for%20a%20comprehensive%20water%20quality%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%97%8F%20ESP32%20Microprocessor%3A%20Powers%20the%20device%20with%20efficient%20processing%20and%20communication%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%97%8F%20Hybrid%20Power%20System%3A%20Ensures%20adaptability%20to%20different%20environments%2C%20reducing%20reliance%20on%20a%20single%20power%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%97%8F%20AI%20Integration%3A%20Designed%20to%20incorporate%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20enhancing%20data%20analysis%20and%20predictive%