s%20advance%2C%20they%20promise%20to%20revolutionise%20our%20understanding%20and%20management%20of%20water%20resources%20and%20sanitation.%20For%20example%2C%20based%20on%20trained%20data%20it%20can%20predict%20pre%20and%20post-monsoon%20water%20parameters%20range%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-Presentation-1707316174.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IIT%20Guwahati%20PhD%20scholar%20develops%20IoT-enabled%20water%20quality%20measuring%20device%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-Presentation-1707316174.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-Presentation-1707316174-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-Presentation-1707316174-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-Presentation-1707316174-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-Presentation-1707316174-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341096%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESatyam%20presenting%20his%20innovation%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20makes%20this%20device%20so%20affordable%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Satyam%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20cost%20reduction%20of%20our%20device%20to%20Rs%2012