e%20started%20playing%20tennis%2C%20a%20sport%20she%20loved.%20In%20the%20first%20few%20days%20itself%2C%20she%20saw%20her%20mood%20changing%20and%20began%20feeling%20better.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20joined%20zumba%20classes%20and%20as%20she%20felt%20more%20confident%2C%20she%20enrolled%20in%20a%20gym.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWorking%20out%20releases%20endorphins%2C%20a%20happy%20hormone%20that%20makes%20you%20feel%20great.%20I%20felt%20more%20present%20at%20home%20after%20doing%20something%20for%20myself%20and%20I%20slowly%20started%20understanding%20fitness%20and%20got%20deeper%20into%20it.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20losing%20weight%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20building%20muscles%20and%20improving%20your%20overall%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Moushmi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20became%20happy%20and%20content%2C%20her%20children%20modelled%20her%20behaviour.%20Soon%2C%20Moushmi%20started%20following%20her%20passions%2C%20which%20included%20biking%20and%20trekking.%20She%20bought%20a%20bike%20for%20herself%20in%202013%20and%20started%20going%20on%20long%20solo%20rides.%20She%20also%20started%20her%20own%20venture%2C%20an%20event%20decor%20company%2C%20and%20worked%20as%20a%20professional%20photographer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBiking%20gives%20me%20a%20sense%20of%20freedom.%20It%20feels%20meditative%20and%20makes%20me%20feel%20independent.%20Travelling%20gives%20me%20a%20different%20perspective%20on%20life.%20I%20also%20started%20challenging%20my%20limitations%20by%20trekking.%20Every%20trek%20feels%20like%20an%20attempt%20to%20conquer%20our%20physical%20and%20mental%20obstacles%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoushmi%20had%20support%20from%20her%20in-laws%20as%20she%20embarked%20on%20these%20trips.%20Her%20children%2C%20too%2C%20learnt%20to%20be%20independent.%20Vedansh%20also%20started%20attending%20school.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20helped%20me%20give%20my%20kids%20direction%20and%20mot