%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20homestay%20offers%20home-cooked%20authentic%20Himachali%20food.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20activities%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20offer%20four%20to%20five%20activities%20as%20part%20of%20our%20package.%20Guests%20can%20enjoy%20a%20guided%20tour%20of%20the%20forest%20park%2C%20included%20in%20the%20package%2C%20during%20the%20morning%20or%20evening.%20We%20also%20take%20them%20to%20a%20secluded%2C%20hidden%20viewpoint%20with%20breathtaking%20views.%20Here%2C%20guests%20can%20indulge%20in%20a%20picnic%2C%20savour%20tea%2C%20and%20soak%20in%20the%20remarkable%20scenery.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20has%20three%20hikes%20that%20the%20people%20can%20experience.%20She%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20offer%20three%20additional%20hiking%20options%3A%20Lion%20King%20Rock%2C%20a%20one-hour%20hike%3B%20Lamaduk%2C%20a%20four-hour%20trek%3B%20and%20Rani%20Su%20Lake%2C%20a%20full-day%20hike.%20Guests%20can%20enjoy%20these%20excursions%20at%20an%20additional%20cost.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20these%20treks%2C%20Heena%20makes%20sure%20there%20is%20no%20plastic%20waste%20discarded%20by%20her%20guests.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20our%20duty%20to%20maintain%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20hills.%20On%20my%20way%20back%2C%20we%20also%20collect%20the%20garbage%20we%20find%20on%20the%20path%20to%20keep%20the%20surroundings%20clean%20and%20green%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUmang%20Thebaria%2C%20who%20visited%20Afsana%20Homestay%2C%20has%20some%20wonderful%20things%20to%20share%20about%20his%20stay.%20%E2%80%9COne%20word%20that%20sums%20up%20my%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20home.%20It%20was%20so%20cosy%20and%20home-like%20that%20we%20decided%20to%20miss%20our%20bus%20only%20to%20stay%20a%20few%20more%20hours%20on%20the%20balcony%20and%20soak%20in%20the%20silence.%20The%20delicious%20meals%20that%20Ludramani%20Bhai%20Ji%20made%20for%20us%20were%20so%