%20finalists%2C%20children%20ranging%20from%20Classes%206%20to%209%2C%20who%20participated%20in%20L%26amp%3BT%E2%80%99s%20National%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330277%2Fbengaluru-startup-stemonsters-founder-dr-sonali-dasgupta-making-science-fun-for-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESTEM%20Challenge%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20a%20culmination%20of%20the%20conglomerate%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Engineering%20Futures%E2%80%99%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%202020%2C%20this%20initiative%20aims%20to%20cultivate%20science%2C%20technology%2C%20engineering%2C%20and%20mathematics%20(STEM)%20interest%20among%20school%20children.%20By%20reaching%20out%20to%20schools%20that%20lack%20access%20to%20STEM%20labs%2C%20children%20in%20remote%20corners%20of%20the%20country%20are%20now%20able%20to%20enhance%20their%20scientific%20knowledge%2C%20grasp%20essential%20concepts%2C%20and%20develop%20problem-solving%20skills%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20school%20teachers%2C%20the%20remarkable%20outcome%20of%20this%20initiative%20is%20that%20even%20children%20who%20typically%20struggled%20in%20exams%20are%20now%20able%20to%20unleash%20their%20creativity%20and%20understand%20science%20concepts%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20traditional%20teaching%20methods%20often%20fall%20short%20of%20achieving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20winners%20%E2%80%94%20Joshwa%20A%20and%20Sivakarthikeyan%20N%20from%20Class%208%20at%20Government%20High%20School%2C%20Gerugambakkam%2C%20Chennai%20%E2%80%94%20ingeniously%20crafted%20the%20agricultural%20tricycle%20by%20repurposing%20an%20old%20cycle%2C%20scrap%20metal%2C%20and%20wheels%20acquired%20from%20a%20local%20scrap%20shop.%20Their%20teacher%2C%20Thenmughil%20Ramakrishnan%2C%20was%20initially%20surprised%20to%20see%20the%20boys%20transporting%20scrap%20materials%20to%20their%20homes%20daily.%20It%20was%20only%20later%20that%20she%20discovered%20they%20were%20constructing%20a%20device%20to%20assist%20farmers%20in%20performing%20multiple%20tasks%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20boys%20were%20in%20Class%206%20when%20the%20pandemic%20started.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20L%26amp%3BT%20started%20providing%20online%20classes%20to%20teach%20science%2C%20arts%20and%20maths.%20The%20students%20were%20given%20easy%20ways%20to%20make%20simple%20projects%20at%20home%2C%20which%20kept%20them%20occupied%20while%20they%20learnt%20the%20important%20concepts%2C%E2%80%9D%20Thenmughil%20tells%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%20that%20despite%20facing%20challenges%20in%20writing%20Tamil%20or%20English%20proficiently%2C%20these%20boys%20exhibit%20a%20remarkable%20understanding%20of%20science%20concepts.%20They%20independently%20constructed%20the%20entire%20device%2C%20delving%20into%20areas%20of%20agriculture%2C%20engineering%2C%20and%20beyond%20%E2%80%94%20showcasing%20their%20adeptness%20in%20practical%20knowledge%20and%20hands-on%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2024%20teams%20(50%20children)%20from%20Chennai%2C%20Coimbatore%2C%20Hazira%2C%20Vadodara%2C%20Talegaon%20and%20Mumbai%20made%20it%20to%20the%20finals%2C%20which%20was%20conducted%20in%20Mumbai%20on%203%20February%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20STEM%20activities%20around%20existing%20curriculums%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201500px)%20100vw%2C%201500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140935.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22By%20connecting%20with%20underserved%20schools%20without%20STEM%20labs%2C%20children%20in%20remote%20areas%20can%20now%20improve%20their%20scientific%20knowledge.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140935.jpeg%201500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140935-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140935-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140935-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140935-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340837%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBy%20connecting%20with%20underserved%20schools%20without%20STEM%20labs%2C%20children%20in%20remote%20areas%20can%20now%20improve%20their%20scientific%20knowledge.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility%20(CSR)%20initiatives%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20has%20been%20actively%20involved%20in%20the%20education%20sector%20for%20over%20three%20decades.%20Recognising%20that%20nearly%2080%20percent%20of%20future%20jobs%20will%20require%20science%20and%20math%20skills%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20aims%20to%20address%20the%20challenge%20of%20limited%20access%20and%20resources%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMabel%20Abraham%2C%20Head%20%E2%80%93%20Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility%20at%20L%26amp%3BT%2C%20explained%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20focus%20on%20STEM%20was%20made%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EL%26amp%3BT%20has%20undertaken%20a%20comprehensive%20approach%20to%20facilitate%20access%20to%20STEM%20education%20in%20government%20schools%20and%20schools%20with%20limited%20resources.%20This%20initiative%20is%20designed%20to%20bridge%20the%20gap%20and%20ensure%20that%20students%20have%20the%20necessary%20tools%20and%20opportunities%20to%20develop%20skills%20essential%20for%20the%20evolving%20job%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20different%20models%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20STEM%20education%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302015%2Fboson-whitewater-bengaluru-startup-converts-stp-water-to-high-quality-potable-drinking-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20science%20labs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20implementing%20digital%20classrooms%2C%20and%20providing%20DIY%20kits%2C%20among%20other%20approaches.%20We%20did%20not%20want%20to%20focus%20on%20just%20one%20model%2C%20and%20instead%2C%20we%20decided%20on%20a%20blended%20approach%2C%20working%20to%20address%20the%20specific%20needs%20of%20each%20school%20as%20cracking%20just%20one%20piece%20of%20the%20puzzle%20is%20not%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mabel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmbracing%20the%20Smart%20School%20concept%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20initially%20focussed%20on%20furnishing%20schools%20with%20fundamental%20infrastructure%20before%20progressing%20to%20the%20establishment%20of%20STEM%20labs.%20However%2C%20their%20original%20plan%20underwent%20adjustments%20due%20to%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20pandemic%20coinciding%20with%20the%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommencing%20with%2065%20schools%20nationwide%2C%20it%20pivoted%20to%20online%20classes%20and%20modules%20in%20response%20to%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20COVID-19.%20The%20volunteers%20distributed%20WhatsApp%20videos%20and%20assigned%20children%20straightforward%20DIY%20projects%20that%20could%20be%20completed%20using%20materials%20readily%20available%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Teachers%20note%20that%20these%20models%20not%20only%20let%20students%20display%20creativity%20but%20also%20assist%20in%20delivering%20more%20effective%20explanations%2C%20using%20the%20visual%20aids%20provided%20by%20the%20projects.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969-768x432.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969-1536x864.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1707140969-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340838%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETeachers%20note%20that%20these%20models%20not%20only%20let%20students%20display%20creativity%20but%20also%20assist%20in%20delivering%20more%20effective%20explanations%2C%20using%20the%20visual%20aids%20provided%20by%20the%20projects.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChildren%20were%20excited%20to%20do%20the%20projects%20and%20they%20would%20share%20it%20eagerly.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20even%20hosted%20an%20online%20science%20fair%20to%20showcase%20their%20creations.%20We%20were%20amazed%20by%20the%20projects%20they%20came%20up%20with%3B%20it%20fired%20their%20creativity%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Mabel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EL%26amp%3BT%20collaborates%20with%20local%20NGO%20partners%20to%20implement%20the%20programme%20in%20selected%20schools%2C%20committing%20to%20support%20these%20schools%20for%20at%20least%20three%20to%20four%20years.%20The%20initiative%20works%20on%20dual%20fronts%20%E2%80%94%20providing%20training%20to%20teachers%20in%20STEM%20education%20and%20building%20physical%20infrastructure%20in%20schools%2C%20including%20STEM%20labs%20or%20digital%20classrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20begins%20with%20L%26amp%3BT%20selecting%20a%20school%2C%20and%20conducting%20an%20orientation%20and%20a%20needs%20assessment.%20A%20key%20criterion%20is%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20science%20teacher%2C%20and%20the%20initiative%20is%20tailored%20for%20students%20in%20Classes%206%20to%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20through%20NGO%20partners%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20delivers%20training%20to%20the%20district%20education%20officer%2C%20school%20principal%2C%20and%20teachers.%20Quarterly%20training%20sessions%20are%20conducted%20for%20teachers%2C%20with%20an%20observer%20present%20in%20the%20classroom%20to%20evaluate%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20teaching%20and%20provide%20guidance%20on%20improvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20hands-on%20approach%20not%20only%20equips%20teachers%20to%20impart%20knowledge%20effectively%20but%20also%20strives%20to%20establish%20a%20sustainable%20model.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20empower%20teachers%20to%20continue%20delivering%20quality%20education%20independently%2C%20even%20without%20ongoing%20assistance%20from%20the%20NGO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20idea%20is%20to%20improve%20children%E2%80%99s%20conceptual%20understanding%20of%20science.%20Based%20on%20our%20observation%2C%20many%20students%20lose%20interest%20in%20science%20in%20Classes%206%20to%209.%20Girl%20students%20too%20face%20several%20biases%20and%20challenges%20as%20STEM%20courses%20are%20not%20traditionally%20considered%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20domain.%20If%20they%20get%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20scientific%20concepts%20through%20innovative%20methods%2C%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20of%20them%20choosing%20a%20career%20in%20science%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Mabel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdapting%20to%20the%20specific%20needs%20and%20interests%20of%20each%20school%20management%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20enhances%20the%20physical%20infrastructure%20based%20on%20demand.%20What%20started%20with%2065%20schools%20has%20now%20expanded%20to%20include%20208%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeachers%20share%20that%20the%20presence%20of%20these%20models%20not%20only%20allows%20students%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340084%2Fgujarat-school-for-the-blind-and-visually-impaired-inclusive-design-architecture-by-anand-sonecha-sealabs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshowcase%20their%20creativity%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20also%20aids%20teachers%20in%20delivering%20more%20effective%20explanations%2C%20utilising%20the%20visual%20aids%20provided%20by%20the%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20we%20would%20just%20explain%20concepts%2C%20with%20children%20not%20being%20able%20to%20see%20how%20it%20works.%20Through%20these%20models%20and%20kits%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20demonstrate%20how%20the%20concept%20works%2C%20helping%20in%20easier%20understanding.%20Children%20also%20ask%20more%20questions.%20The%20concept%20reaches%20them%20easily%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Veeramuthu%20N%2C%20a%20teacher%20from%20Government%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%2C%20Kaliannanpudur%2C%20Coimbatore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20L%26amp%3BT%20has%20provided%20them%20with%2075%20kits%2C%20which%20include%20working%20models%2C%20explanatory%20models%20and%20charts.%20Children%20are%20taken%20to%20the%20lab%2C%20where%20they%20can%20experiment.%20Alternatively%2C%20teachers%20also%20bring%20the%20models%20to%20class%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20concept%20they%20are%20teaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20NGO%20partners%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20the%20American%20India%20Foundation%20(AIF)%20and%20Don%20Bosco%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20%E2%80%94%20offer%20after-school%20classes%20for%20students.%20These%20sessions%20cover%20a%20range%20of%20topics%2C%20including%20mobile%20application%20development%2C%20coding%2C%20CNC%20machining%2C%20sensors%2C%20map%20making%2C%203D%20printing%2C%20and%20more.%20The%20knowledge%20gained%20in%20the