ishers%E2%80%9D%20questioned%20her%20mother%20about%20why%20she%20was%20sending%20her%20daughter%20to%20Mumbai%2C%20considering%20her%20dream%20(of%20having%20a%20child%20studying%20at%20IIT)%20was%20already%20achieved.%20In%20response%2C%20her%20mother%20simply%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CLet%20her%20do%20whatever%20she%20wants.%20Both%20my%20children%20are%20equal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333216%2Fiit-guwahati-invents-sensor-for-diabetes-diet-low-glycemic-index-food%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIIT%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20entrepreneurial%20bug%20took%20birth%20inside%20the%20chemical%20engineer.%20Furthermore%2C%20being%20part%20of%20the%20entrepreneurship%20cell%20and%20the%20theatre%20group%20in%20college%20changed%20her%20outlook%20towards%20life.%20%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20one%20day%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20brand%20from%20scratch.%20Storytelling%2C%20to%20me%2C%20is%20powerful%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20share%20my%20story%20through%20a%20brand.%20I%20decided%20it%20should%20be%20in%20the%20consumer%20goods%20industry%2C%20even%20though%20I%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20figured%20out%20the%20specifics%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20while%20studying%20at%20IIT%2C%20Ahana%E2%80%99s%20eating%20habits%20remained%20poor%20as%20she%20resorted%20to%20junk.%20She%20would%20fall%20sick%20often%2C%20be%20it%20at%20school%20or%20college%2C%20without%20realising%20that%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20was%20the%20food%20she%20consumed.%20It%20would%20be%20four%20years%20later%20at%20Harvard%20when%20she%20would%20come%20to%20the%20realisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Why%20does%20India%20lack%20healthy%20packaged%20food%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%2